OL,3,CFailed Derby County bidder Chris
OL,4,CKirchner sentenced to 20 years in
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FAmerican businessman Chris Kirchner,
OL,8,Fwho was close to buying Derby County,
OL,9,Fhas been handed a 20-year prison
OL,10,Fsentence for defrauding investors of
OL,11,Ftens of millions of dollars.
OL,13,FMr. Kirchner, 37, founded supply chain
OL,14,Fmanagement software company Slync in
OL,15,F2017.
OL,17,FHe held the position of CEO until his
OL,18,Ftermination by the Board of Directors
OL,19,Fin 2022, and was initially charged in
OL,20,FFebruary 2023.
