OL,3,CFailed Derby County bidder Chris
OL,4,CKirchner sentenced to 20 years in
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FIn January, the 36-year-old was found
OL,8,Fguilty on four counts of wire fraud
OL,9,Fand an additional seven counts of
OL,10,Fmoney laundering.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced on Thursday (11 July)
OL,13,Fto 20 years in prison and was also
OL,14,Fordered to pay more than $65 million
OL,15,Fin restitution.
OL,17,FKirchner was close to becoming the
OL,18,Fowner of Derby County back in 2022
OL,19,Fwhen the club went into administration.
